---
title: Double Sichuan-Glazed Pork Rissoles with Potato Fries & Asian Pear Slaw
description: Sichuan garlic paste has got to be our new favourite way to flavour. Let’s use it with a splash of soy sauce to coat juicy pork rissoles, what could be better! A side of crispy oven-baked fries add even more fun to this mouth-watering meal.
